ss=\"header-entryBtn-link\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp73705/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"header-entryBtn-sp-none\">新卒採用</span>ENTRY</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n                        <div class=\"pageHeader\">\n                <div class=\"pageHeader-bg\">\n                    <img class=\"pageHeader-img display-sp-none\" src=\"https://www.nds-infos.co.jp/recruit/ndsinfos-sys/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/main-26-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                    <img class=\"pageHeader-img display-pc-none\" src=\"https://www.nds-infos.co.jp/recruit/ndsinfos-sys/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/main-sp-27.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"pageHeader-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"pageHeader-wrap\">\n                        <div class=\"pageHeader-heading\">\n                            <h1 class=\"pageHeader-ttl\">育児・介護支援</h1>\n                            <p class=\"pageHeader-ttl-en\">Care</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"pageHeader-tag\">\n\n                                                    </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"pankuzu\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <ul class=\"pankuzu-list\">\n                    <li class=\"pankuzu-item\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.nds-infos.co.jp/recruit/\" class=\"pankuzu-link\">TOP</a>\n                    </li>\n                                            <li class=\"pankuzu-item\">\n                            <a href=\"https://www.nds-infos.co.jp/recruit/works/\" class=\"pankuzu-link\">職場を知る</a>\n                        </li>\n                                        <li class=\"pankuzu-item\">育児・介護支援</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <main ><div id=\"care\">\r\n<section class=\"care\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-xl heading-border2\">育児支援制度</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tab-contents\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-contents__box\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-contens__box--inner show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-flex\">\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">出生時育児休業<br />（産後パパ育休）</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt class=\"only\">期間</dt>\r\n<dd>子の出生後8週間以内のうち4週間（28日）を限度</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">育児休業</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt class=\"only\">期間</dt>\r\n<dd>1歳迄<br class=\"display-sp-none\" />（条件により2歳）</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">育児短時間勤務</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>中学校入学まで</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>2時間以内</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">育児始終業時刻変更</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>小学校入学まで</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>1日2時間の繰上げ・繰下げ</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">育児深夜勤務免除</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>小学校入学まで</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>22時〜5時免除</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">育児時間外免除</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>3歳未満1回につき<br />1ヶ月以上1年以内範囲</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>時間外労働の免除</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">育児時間外勤務制限</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>小学校入学まで</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>24時間/月・150時間/年</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">看護休暇</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>小学校入学まで</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>子1人：5日/年<br />2人以上：10日/年</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"special-holiday\">\r\n<p class=\"heading heading-l\">(その他)<br />応援金の支給</p>\r\n<p>育児休業の取得期間に応じて、「応援金」が支給されます。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"special-holiday\">\r\n<p class=\"heading heading-l\">特別休暇</p>\r\n<p>配偶者の出産および出生後8週間までの子を育児するとき　5日<br />子育てのために必要なとき(小学校就業前の子育て、「子の看護、通院、行事参加」「配偶者の育児支援」)　子1人につき1日/年</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"care\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-xl heading-border2\">介護支援制度</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tab-contents\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-contents__box\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-contens__box--inner show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-flex\">\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">介護休業</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt class=\"only\">期間</dt>\r\n<dd>1年以内</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">介護短時間勤務</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>3年以内</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>2時間以内</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">介護深夜勤務免除</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>1ヶ月以上6ヶ月以内</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>22時～5時免除</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">介護時間外免除</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>1回につき1ヶ月以上 1年以内範囲</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>時間外労働の免除</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">介護時間外勤務制限</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl class=\"tab-top\">\r\n<dt>期間</dt>\r\n<dd>1ヶ月以上1年以内</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"tab-bottom\">\r\n<dt>適用<br />内容</dt>\r\n<dd>24時間/月・150時間/年</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tabinner-box\">\r\n<p class=\"tab-ttl\">介護休暇</p>\r\n<div class=\"tab-list\">\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt class=\"only\">該当<br />家族</dt>\r\n<dd>1人：5日/年<br />2人以上：10日/年</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <section class=\"cards-section\">\n                        <h3 class=\"heading heading-xl heading-border2\">職場を知る</h3>\n                        <div class=\"cards\">\n                            <div class=\"cards-list cards-list-3\">\n                                                                <div class=\"cards-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"card\">\n                                        <a class=\"card-link\" href=\"https://www.nds-infos.co.jp/recruit/works/welfare/\">\n                                            <div class=\"card-thumbnail\">\n                                                <img src=\"https://www.nds-infos.co.jp/recruit/ndsinfos-sys/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/img-thumbnail-welfare.jpg\" alt=\"\"\n                                                    class=\"card-image\">\n                                            </div>\n                                            <h4 class=\"card-title\">福利厚生</h4>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div><!-- cards-item -->\n                                                                <div class=\"cards-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"card\">\n                                        <a class=\"card-link\" href=\"https://